50|$|On August 13, 1996, Burke {{made his}} <b>big</b> <b>league</b> debut as a 26-year-old rookie. During his <b>big</b> <b>league</b> career, he {{appeared}} {{in a total of}} 28 games and had an ERA of 6.75. He had a record of 4 wins and 6 losses.|$|R
